download tomcat tar .gz file

https://tomcat.apache.org/download-90.cgi  


download jdk tar.gz file

https://www.oracle.com/in/java/technologies/javase/javase8u211-later-archive-downloads.html


download maven

https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi


download jenkins .war file

https://updates.jenkins-ci.org/download/war/



wget jdk/tomcat/maven/jenkins 
tar -xzf resepctive name 




apache-maven-3.8.3             apache-tomcat-9.0.54         hello-world-1  jdk-8u291-linux-x64.tar.gz   
apache-maven-3.8.3-bin.tar.gz  apache-tomcat-9.0.54.tar.gz  jdk1.8.0_291   jenkins.war                 


Update in  .profile for ubuntu

export JAVA_HOME="/opt/jdk1.8.0_291" 
export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH

export M3_HOME="/opt/apache-maven-3.8.3 "
export PATH=$M3_HOME/bin:$PATH

export CATALINA_HOME="/opt/apache-tomcat-9.0.54"
export PATH=$CATALINA_HOME/bin:$PATH	
